# IoT Health Monitoring System

This project monitors patient health parameters using ESP8266.

## Features
- Heart Rate Monitoring
- SpO2 Monitoring
- Temperature Measurement
- Fall Detection using MPU6050
- Blynk IoT Dashboard Monitoring

## Hardware Used
- ESP8266 NodeMCU
- MAX30100 Pulse Oximeter
- MPU6050 Accelerometer
- LCD I2C Display
- Buzzer

## Software Used
- Arduino IDE / VS Code
- Blynk IoT Platform
